'''Now start both {{project_name_gateway_long}} and {{project_name_workstation_long}}'''<br />
[[File:Start both of them7.png|1200px]]

'''Miscellaneous'''

There are also [[Videos|Video Tutorials]].

If you still need help, please check the [[Support|Support]] page.
